    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if those opt-outs mean they don't have to follow laws that protect people? like if a mandate is about healthcare or civil rights, isn't it kind of a problem if a religious group can just say 'no' and ignore the rules everyone else has to follow? wouldn't that undermine equality?",
