    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see your point, but it seems like you're saying the state's version of equality is more important than the individual's right to follow their conscience. if we just ignore religious freedom whenever a law is passed, aren't we basically saying that religious people have to leave their values at the door just to be part of society? isn't that also a kind of unfairness?",
